title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - DeHavilland Dash 7
description:
In this video we will look at version 1.0.3 of the DeHavilland Dash 7. This aircraft is converted from FSX to MSFS 2020. It is still in development phase so please keep that in mind when trying the aircraft.

If you also want to give the aircraft a try you can download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/15835/msfs2020-dehavilland-dash7-dhc7
